Chris Browning https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Browning 0 Chris Browning is an American television and film actor, known for character roles, specializing in more tough and rugged types. However, recent roles have been clean-cut, family-man roles, such as the scientist, Jake, on The CW's The 100, or the ill-equipped father in the Mark Cartier film, Lift Me Up.
